n_District.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.tripadvisor.com.hk%2FRestaurant_Review-g298527-d3734507-Reviews-Rassolnik-Irkutsk_Irkutsk_Oblast_Siberian_District.html&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=e38abc85\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.tripadvisor.com.hk/Restaurant_Review-g298527-d3734507-Reviews-Rassolnik-Irkutsk_Irkutsk_Oblast_Siberian_District.html</a><br />\n伊庫次克必食呢間, <br />\n我食左兩次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大約百幾蚊港紙埋單<br />\n個酥皮白湯世界級<br />\n<br />\n貝加爾湖我求下你袋定小小野食餵狗<br />\n果陣有隻好乖好靚既狗狗係咁嗲我<br />\n日以繼夜 夜以繼日咁跟住我<br />\n餵佢食野又勁斯文<br />\n我真係完全俾佢冧掂但無辦法帶到佢翻黎<br />\n我完全唔知佢地冬天點頂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n翻黎 Search 人地 D 遊記都有見到其他狗都係咁跟住人想食野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TVT4G2k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTVT4G2k.jpg&h=9498097f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食飽傻笑樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢應該成日係 Nikita 搵遊客<br />\n我帶埋佢去舊岩果邊影相"},{"pid":"f81cf084f7575a0d33c8d153813b91e04b175e71","tid":1818200,"uid":221346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48d70d24df14a47917a1025130b77191b48717ca","tid":1818200,"uid":45765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9905dec7275382fcd8266c49d1fecccf2486a11","tid":1818200,"uid":221346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:09:02.000Z","msg":"打算自己一條友去 應唔應該係當地請個導遊好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:11:18.000Z","msg":"我都係自己一個啊 都驚驚地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該4/5月一條友去8-9日 海參崴-貝加爾湖 <br />\n識俄文 應該唔死得掛"},{"pid":"27f19854d5b263673aa6f959690e711bdb2bcb38","tid":1818200,"uid":36692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cb633465b491fc6e130846a08b7cb0bfba38798","tid":1818200,"uid":6815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48d70d24df14a47917a1025130b77191b48717ca","tid":1818200,"uid":45765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9905dec7275382fcd8266c49d1fecccf2486a11","tid":1818200,"uid":221346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:09:02.000Z","msg":"打算自己一條友去 應唔應該係當地請個導遊好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:11:18.000Z","msg":"我都係自己一個啊 都驚驚地"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:17:01.000Z","msg":"係島上Hostel join local tour，個司機就係導遊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:27:34.000Z","msg":"講俄文嘰呢咕嚕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當地我撞到個香港人<br />\n佢話佢 Book 左導遊,<br />\n講到英文. <br />\n同有得玩多 D 野<br />\n冰湖釣魚, 日落騎馬.<br />\n呢 D 自己去唔識 Book, 得 Hostel 南北線<br />\n但睇你 Budget 囉<br />\n除左導遊人工你仲要出埋佢 D 洗費"},{"pid":"cb4f2d9dffa36c82fe658d67a2615de238a177bd","tid":1818200,"uid":36692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"其實自己一個都唔驚<br />\n差唔多全程專車接送<br />\n<br />\n機場入伊庫次克市內用 App call 的士 around $30<br />\n伊庫次克市內巴士我完全黑人問號唔識搭, <br />\n不過唔驚, 地方細, 去邊都行到去, <br />\n大不了的士.<br />\n然後去 Olkon 都係點對點,<br />\nDoor to door 咁接送你.<br />\nBook 好晒野就無野驚<br />\n<br />\n不過我果陣 5 月去, <br />\n天氣無咁凍係輕鬆 D 既"},{"pid":"65e2e9369bb9ef0269212bdf7ca5bc01f77bf7e0","tid":1818200,"uid":81632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:56:02.000Z","msg":"我果時一月頭都係自己去  睇到藍冰<br />\n同埋早啲啲去 果度冰面會乾淨啲<br />\n<br />\n我係海滲葳搭火車去果個鎮  <br />\n<a href=\"http://自己係booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E4%BF%82booking.com&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=109ac605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">自己係booking.com</a> 訂住宿<br />\n再叫hostel啲人幫我安排車 同報tour <br />\n同埋如果hostel有得加錢俾你沖涼既話 <br />\n一定要加  佢係桑拿加沖涼  成桶冰水俾你用<br />\n當體驗下西百利亞人點沖涼<br />\n<br />\n果度物價好平  我成日食佢既雪糕 <br />\n同埋建議係超市買隻 vodka  藍白包裝 用貝加爾湖水整既  好平又幾好飲  <br />\n<br />\n果度平均負廿度  但只要唔好露太多肉都無咩<br />\n我手指腳指長期僵硬  <br />\n同埋好大風 我包到得隻眼露出來<br />\n<br />\n好掛住果度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26a7d534597b7efe92ba33b1aaa0c6629aa91f4","tid":1818200,"uid":6815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:00:17.000Z","msg":"分享d   ios app 俾你地 <br />\n2gis 俄仔地圖<br />\neway 搭公共交通工具無難度"},{"pid":"3d4f04e3ae2e2d4955402187f89677d00ecbf53b","tid":1818200,"uid":135949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"啲藍冰邊個月最靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上網睇啲人都推薦3月頭"},{"pid":"7f02a975906f9454c6fdfa5495afb0523667c4d5","tid":1818200,"uid":45765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d4f04e3ae2e2d4955402187f89677d00ecbf53b","tid":1818200,"uid":135949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"啲藍冰邊個月最靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上網睇啲人都推薦3月頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:06:35.000Z","msg":"但有啲人話3月冇得坐車 2月尾好D"},{"pid":"76b30b26631b90e045e9f014c0c028a952bc07ad","tid":1818200,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:39:09.000Z","msg":"一月去完8日，歡迎入group交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nshare下一月頭嘅相<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/J8d5QxOvJqPTibYTu61Jiw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJ8d5QxOvJqPTibYTu61Jiw&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=2e2ee0ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/J8d5QxOvJqPTibYTu61Jiw</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FpGekbZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFpGekbZ.jpg&h=ac3da9b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nFDDMR0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnFDDMR0.jpg&h=e8497078&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/73Dgyw4.jp